translated:
Östling, Gustav Adolf (Gösta), central librarian, Borås, b. 13/5/02 in Stockholm to Gustaf Ö. and Edla Larsson. Married 1930 to Sigrid Ramström. Children: Sven b. 1931, Kerstin b. 1934, Erik b. 1938, Eva b. 1944. — Bachelor of Arts in Uppsala 1925. Traveled to Denmark 1930. City librarian in Uppsala 1927-1930, central librarian in Borås from 1930. Secretary in the Nordic Association's Borås division 1938-1943, vice-chairman in the Västergöta Sports Association 1943-1946, secretary in the Borås Rotary Club 1943-1947, chairman of the Literary Society in Borås from 1946, board member of the technical gymnasium from 1946, secretary of the Swedish Public Library Association from 1947. Editor of Biblioteksbladet from 1948. Published articles in Biblioteksbladet. Member of the Swedish Research Council. 

Östlund, Crispin Gustaf, dentist, Limmared, b. 25/10/98 in Trollhättan to book printer Lars Johan Ö. and Maria Eleonora Wennergren. Married 1930 to Petra Ingvarda Sörensen. High school graduation in Vänersborg 1918, medical studies 1918-1922, dental candidate 1930, dentist 1933. Practiced in Limmared and Länghem. Vice-chairman of the Odontological Association 1930-1931, chairman and curator 1931-1932.
